onovan and Fintan McCarthy claiming gold medals in Paris.\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 343, \"end\": 355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7422426429150262e-18, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 390, \"end\": 406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhys_McClenaghan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rhys McClenaghan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhys_McClenaghan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhys_McClenaghan\"}, {\"begin\": 418, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_O'Donovan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paul O'Donovan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_O'Donovan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_O'Donovan\"}, {\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fintan McCarthy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\"}, {\"begin\": 477, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994743121, \"rank\": 5.25681779976882e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Harrington's win also officially confirmed a record-breaking seven medals from a single Games for Ireland.\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 485, \"end\": 495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"score\": 0.9997787871301101, \"rank\": 0.00011611386897319516, \"text\": \"Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\"}, {\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999755884804, \"rank\": 2.4411479335200567e-08, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taoiseach Simon Harris said Harrington's success has \\\"lifted the mood of the nation\\\".\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Harris_(politician)\", \"score\": 0.7586345184268454, \"rank\": 0.31788125086095476, \"text\": \"Simon Harris\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Harris_(politician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Harris_(politician)\"}, {\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"score\": 0.9997787871301101, \"rank\": 0.00011611386897319516, \"text\": \"Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People are absolutely ecstatic.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's lifted the mood of the nation.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She has proven herself to be an unrivaled champion.\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's a legend, she's an icon.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's an inspiration to many, many, many young people in her own community, but right across right across Ireland,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 941, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999755884804, \"rank\": 2.4411479335200567e-08, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Taoiseach also took time to praise the wider achievements of the 133 athletes in Ireland's Olympic team, saying they \\\"have just done us so proud\\\".\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 965, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taoiseach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3365706811684484e-34, \"text\": \"Taoiseach\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taoiseach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taoiseach\"}, {\"begin\": 1046, \"end\": 1053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999755884804, \"rank\": 2.4411479335200567e-08, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"T\\u00e1naiste Miche\\u00e1l Martin called Harrington's performance a \\\"boxing masterclass\\\".\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1113, \"end\": 1121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanistry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0873477404073344e-17, \"text\": \"T\\u00e1naiste\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanistry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanistry\"}, {\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.999995157974253, \"rank\": 4.840857170776209e-06, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"