://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\"}, {\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"score\": 0.9997787871301101, \"rank\": 0.00011611386897319516, \"text\": \"Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\"}, {\"begin\": 1430, \"end\": 1435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994743121, \"rank\": 5.25681779976882e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1478, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kellie Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\"}, {\"begin\": 1595, \"end\": 1600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"score\": 0.8257230104555031, \"rank\": 0.20823539891324244, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An inspiration.\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Minister for Sport Catherine Martin also congratulated her and called Harrington a \\\"magnificent fighter\\\".\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1682, \"end\": 1688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.999995157974253, \"rank\": 4.840857170776209e-06, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}, {\"begin\": 1723, \"end\": 1733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"score\": 0.9997787871301101, \"rank\": 0.00011611386897319516, \"text\": \"Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sinn F\\u00e9in leader Mary Lou McDonald meanwhile celebrated the Olympic champion, referring to Harrington as \\\"the pride of Dublin's north inner city.\\\"\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1760, \"end\": 1769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Workers'_Party_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5340892708584412e-21, \"text\": \"Sinn F\\u00e9in\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Workers'_Party_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Workers'_Party_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1777, \"end\": 1794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Lou_McDonald\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mary Lou McDonald\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Lou_McDonald\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Lou_McDonald\"}, {\"begin\": 1851, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"score\": 0.9997787871301101, \"rank\": 0.00011611386897319516, \"text\": \"Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\"}, {\"begin\": 1879, \"end\": 1885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"score\": 0.9999995034166983, \"rank\": 4.688137433539945e-07, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the match,Harrington insisted she retired from boxing.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1928, \"end\": 1938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"score\": 0.9997787871301101, \"rank\": 0.00011611386897319516, \"text\": \"Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's the last hurrah, I am done,\\\" she told RT\\u00c9 Sport.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2020, \"end\": 2029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999789533833, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always said I want to retire a champion.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's it.\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let me just say it once again, Bob's your uncle, Fanny's your aunt, good night Irene'.\\\"\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2123, \"end\": 2126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"score\": 0.99987164271154, \"rank\": 0.000128294074275775, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\"}, {\"begin\": 2141, \"end\": 2146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fanny_Mendelssohn\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.4808364443673625e-13, \"text\": \"Fanny\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fanny_Mendelssohn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fanny_Mendelssohn\"}, {\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goodnight,_Irene\", \"score\": 0.9999999992060111, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"good night Irene\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goodnight,_Irene\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goodnight,_Irene\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A jubilant Harrington said her pre-fight plan was to \\\"just be happy - happy, smile and enjoy it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2192, \"end\": 2202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"score\": 0.9997787871301101, \"rank\": 0.00011611386897319516, \"text\": \"Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting further on what her medal meant to her community and the country as a whole, the 34-year-old added: \\\"It just gives hope.\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All these young kids all these teenagers, it give hope to them, it gives hope to the people of Ireland, that's what it means.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2507, \"end\": 2514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999755884804, \"rank\": 2.4411479335200567e-08, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this one was for me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Source:PA    \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Ra